Pascal Okechukwu a ma dịka 'Cubana Chiefpriest' bụ otimkpu a ma ama na onye ndụmọdụ pụrụiche nke Gọvanọ Uzodimma nke Imo steeti n'okwu soshal midia.
Okechukwu, onye aha ya na-akpọtụ ugbua na soshal midia bụ onye a ma dịka ore mmanya ndị ọgaranya (celebrity barman), nakwa enyi ahụghị ma erịghị nke Obi Iyiegbu a ma dịka Obi Cubana.

Paschal Okechukwu a ma dịka Cubana Chiefpriest bụ otimkpu a ma ama
Cubana Chiefpriest malitere iwu na soshal midia n'ụtụtụ ụbọchị ụka 4 Eprel, 2022 maka akụkọ sị na ụlọọrụ na-ebuagha megide mpụ bụ EFCC nwuchiri ya.
Akụkọ sị na EFCC boro ya ebubo ibupu ego n'ụzọ na-ezighi ezi nakwa ịgbanahụ ụtụisi, mana BBC Igbo e nweghi ike ịkọwa ma ọ bụ eziokwu.
Mgbe BBC Igbo kpọrọ ọnụ na-ekwuru ụlọọrụ EFCC bụ Wilson Owujaren, ọ zaghị, n'otu aka ahụ ekwentị Cubana Chiefpriest gbanyụrụ agbanyụ oge a kpọrọ ya.
Ụbọchị abụọ nke ọnwa Eprel kwesịrị ịbụ ụbọchị ncheta ọmụmụ Chiefpriest mana o nweghi ozi ọbụla o wepụtara na soshal midia banyere ya.
Kamgbe ụbọchị anọ gara aga o nwebeghi ozi ọbụla o wepụtarala n'akara Instagram ya bụ ebe ọ na-ewepụta ozi kwa mgbe kwa mgbe.
Ebe foto si, Cubana Chiefpriest
Cubana Chief Priest bụ onye enyemaka pụrụ iche nye Gọvanọ Hope Uzodinma nke Imo Steeti

Cubana Chief Priest bụ onye na-ahazibu ụlọọrụ 'Cubana Group' nke gụnyere: 'Grand Cubana Hotel'; Rolex Hotel; Cubana Night Club; Pablo Cubana; Crave Cubana; Opium Cubana; Gustavo Cubana; Cubana Leisure na ndị ọzọ.
A nwuchiburu ya n'afọ 2020, maka ebubo na o ji ndị nchekwa uweojii '(Police Escort) eme ka o siri masị ya.
Ebe foto si, Cubana Chiefpriest/Instagram

A ma ya dịka onye na-eme ihe ego ma na-egosikwa na o ji 'nkụ' I ji maa atụ, o nyere enyi ya nwoke bụ Obinna Iyiegbu (Obi Cubana) ehi 46 oge ọ kwara nne ya n'afọ 2021.Akụkọ kwuru na o nwere ụgbọala ndị oke ọnụahịa dịka: Rolls Royce Phantom, Toyota Prado, Mercedes Benz G-class na Range Rover.
Cubana Chief Priest na-egosikwa akụnaụba ya nke ukwuu na soshal midia.
Ọ bụ onye Umuhu Okabia dị n'Okpuru Ọchịchị Orsu n'Imo steeti
O toro n'Aba, Abia steeti
Ọ gara akwụkwọ n'ụlọakwụkwọ dị elu, "Federal Polytechnic Nekede'.
O bidoro ndụ ya dịka onye na-arụ akpụkpọụkwụ na otiegwu mana ọ chakeghị rue oge ọ banyere n'ọrụ otimkpu na onye na-ahazị ụlọnkwarị ndị nwere agba
Ọ malitere ịhazi ụlọọrụ nkwarị nke Cubana Group.
O mechara malite ụlọrụ nkwarị nke ya ọ kpọrọ "Club Xhrine n'afọ 2020.
Ọ lụọla nwaanyị ma jiri ụmụ nwoke abụọ.
Agaghị m akwado onye ọbụla na-agbasa ozi ka e gbuo mmadụ n'ụzọ ọbụla, nke mere ndị Ipob ji kpọọ m asị – Uche Mefor
